																<a href="mailto:?subject=Independent%20Author%20Index%20%3A%20How%20can%20I%20set%20my%20eBook%20price%20to%20%240.00%20on%20Amazon%3F&body=Check%20out%20this%20article%3A%20How%20can%20I%20set%20my%20eBook%20price%20to%20%240.00%20on%20Amazon%3F%20-%20http%3A%2F%2Findaindex.com%2Fhow-can-i-set-my-ebook-price-to-0-00-on-amazon%2F" target="_blank" title="How can I set my eBook price to $0.00 on Amazon?" class="small-button"><span class="icon-text">&#9993;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Send e-mail</a>
